paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, south, southwest, west
description: Several buckets lie in piles, some upright, others overturned.  Their pale silver color reflects the moonlight and shoots out a show of brilliant light at some angles.  A few ramshackle booths are decorated with colorful ribbons and bunches of flowers.  Nearby, the fields are full of rhubarb in full bloom and ready for the harvest.
